        "S45 SINGLE SHADE",
        "S45 SINGLE SHADE W/3\" POCKET",
        "S45 SINGLE SHADE W/4\" POCKET",
        "S45 CF90 FASCIA",
        "S45 W/ SQUARE CASSETTE 110",
        "S45 DUAL SHADE",
        "S45 COUPLED SHADE",
        "S45 DUAL COUPLED SHADE",
        "COULISSE ABSOLUTE OPEN ROLL",
